  "texts": [
    "The predictions from the previous step can be used to enhance the Planning and Evaluator modules by incorporating Belief as an additional input.",
    "To optimize costs, we merge the Planning and Evaluator modules.",
    "A sample prompt template for the new Planning and Evaluator modules can be found in B.2, and the sample outputs of this part can be found in C.",
    "Planning with Second Order ToM: Skilled card game players excel at dynamically adapting their tactics, potentially tricking opponents into making suboptimal plays.",
